      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a script for a new gritty crime thriller. I need help setting the scene for one of the main locations—it's this really rough, dangerous part of the city that's basically seen better days. Can you write a paragraph describing the area? I want it to feel intense and show the social decay and the sense of tension that residents feel just walking down the street. Just need some vivid sensory details to get the mood right.",
